---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ContactCard from "../components/ContactCard.astro";
import TechnologiesCard from "../components/TechnologiesCard.astro";
import "../styles/index.css";
---

<Layout title="Arael | Portfolio">
	<main>
		<div class="w-full text-center mb-1">
			<h1 class="pb-5 text-4xl">Welcome to <span class="text-gradient">my portfolio.</span></h1>
		</div>
		<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
			<ContactCard
				href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jonasgroening/"
				title="My LinkedIn"
				body="Connect with me!"
				target="_blank"
			/>
			<ContactCard
				href="https://github.com/arael34/"
				title="My GitHub"
				body="Check out some source code."
				target="_blank"
			/>
			<!--
			<Card
				href="/portfolio/blog"
				title="Blog"
				body="I barely write anything."
			/>
			<Card
				href="/portfolio/about"
				title="Contact me"
				body="Want to get in touch?"
			/> -->
		</ul>
		<div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl my-7 text-center">Experience</h1>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap">
				<div class="text-box w-1/2">
					<h3 class="text-xl">Co-Founder at Quarry.video</h3>
					<p>
						I'm currently building a tool to help video editors work more efficiently. 
						You can visit the WIP at <a href="https://quarry.video" target="_blank">quarry.video.</a>
						I've spent countless hours building features and designing the UI.
					</p>
					<br /> <!-- Remove this -->
					<h3 class="text-xl">Technologies</h3>
					<div class="flex">
						<TechnologiesCard name="NextJS" src="/nextjs.svg" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="Golang" src="/golang.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="React" src="/react.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="Tailwind" src="/tailwind.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="Django" src="/django.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="MongoDB" src="/mongodb.png" />
					</div>
				</div>
				<img src="/LandingPage.png" class="mx-auto my-5" />
				<img src="/SnippetViewer.png" class="mx-auto my-5" />
				<div class="text-box w-1/2">
					<p>
						My contributions include but aren't limited to: building the frontend
						with NextJS, creating and hosting a centralized logging service with Go,
						and writing a database abstraction for our Django backend to safely make
						database calls.
					</p>
					<br /> <!-- Remove this -->
					<h3 class="text-xl">Technologies, cont.</h3>
					<div class="flex">
						<TechnologiesCard name="Docker" src="/docker.webp" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="Redis" src="/redis.jpg" />
					</div>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap">
				<div class="text-box w-1/2">
					<h3 class="text-xl">Software Engineering Intern at CriTech Research, Inc.</h3>
					<p>
						Over the summer, I'm working full time at CriTech Research, Inc. as an
						intern. Currently, I'm refactoring a legacy C# .NET codebase to make
						a more secure system. I also created a CI/CD pipeline with Jenkins to
						continually test and deploy the codebase.
					</p>
					<br /> <!-- Remove this -->
					<h3 class="text-xl">Technologies</h3>
					<div class="flex">
						<TechnologiesCard name="C#" src="/csharp.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name=".NET" src="/dotnet.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="Jenkins" src="/jenkins.png" />
						<TechnologiesCard name="React" src="/react.png" />
					</div>
				</div>
				<img src="/CriTech.jpg" class="mx-auto my-auto" />
			</div>
		</div>
		<div>
			<h1 class="text-4xl my-7 text-center">Projects</h1>
			<div class="text-box w-1/2">
				<h3 class="text-xl">MonkeyType-Friends</h3>
				<p>
					I wanted to compete with my friends in MonkeyType, so I'm making
					a website to do it. The source code can be seen
					<a href="https://github.com/arael34/monkeytype-friends" target="_blank">
						here.
					</a>
					This is still a WIP.
				</p>
			</div>	
			<div class="text-box w-1/2">
				<h3 class="text-xl">QLogger</h3>
				<p>
					I built a centralized logging service for Quarry.video. It's written in Go and uses
					MongoDB as a database. It's currently hosted on railway. Check out the repo
					<a href="https://github.com/arael34/qlogger" target="_blank">
						here.
					</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="text-box w-1/2">
				<h3 class="text-xl">Concept Map Browser Extension</h3>
				<p>
					This is a collaborative project for a school club. It's a browser extension that
					allows you to highlight text and generate an interactive concept map from it.
					Check out the repo
					<a href="https://github.com/kuldeep7688/concept-map-browser-extension" target="_blank">
						here.
					</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="text-box w-1/2">
				<h3 class="text-xl">Various Rust simulations</h3>
				<p>I wanted to learn rust, so I made a few simulations.</p>
				<h4>A port of pipes.sh</h4>
				<h4>Physarum simulation</h4>
				<h4>Quadtree Nbody simulation</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
